<emphasis id="60E236EE083F5150697B82110B9B4436" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="94">S. paraergatensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<emphasis id="EDC24F9BD73FA231FAA144934378B137" bold="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="94">A</emphasis>
budding cells 
